title: FANTOM Listing: Add BOO market
body:
Intro: This is a vote to list BOO on C.R.E.A.M. Fantom market with a Collateral Factor and Collateral Cap.
Proposal: Listing Committee
Rational: First mover advantage

For: 
Add BOO market with Collateral Factor: 65% and Collateral Cap: $4M

Against: 
Do not make any changes to FANTOM market.
author: 0x81f8CaBe89066d43EB4faFD8E4E5256C102E6E30
